body:
can someone be so nice as to explain to me where is this ferocious hatred for mcu clint coming from?
i get that one can dislike the way his character is developped or the way the actor plays him but going after the way he looks or making assumptions such as “he looks like he’s homophobic/republican”? like,,,, why? i genuinely don’t understand.
